Jul 7 2009 	Best place to stay in London - and I mean it.	This large, friendly and service-minded aparthotel did nothing less than accommodate my all wishes and expectations from the moment I stepped in the door. Location: The apartments are located in beautiful white villas on a quiet and leafy street 30sec from Queensway Underground Station (this means 5min by tube to central, and there are also many frequent night buses). It is just across from the best part of Hyde Park, and there are many local cafés, bars and restaurants 2mins walk from the apartments.In my opinion, you don't get a better location in London for that kind of money and I've been visiting the city at least once a month in the last 6 years.Facilities: The room we had was just perfect and exactly what I had had in mind. It's always difficult to book self-catering apartments and judge a place by its photos, but I still prefer an homely and 'personal' holiday apartment to a hotel that can make you feel like you are just in transit. The kitchen was perfectly stocked with lots of utilities for cooking, and the bathroom was really clean. The living/bedroom had a stylish decor, quality furniture and a massive window allowing in plenty of sunlight. Our flat also came with cheap pay-as-you-go wifi, but I'm not sure if that goes for all of the apartments.Service: The main reception for all of the apartments is a nice and cosy office where the staff is both professional and very friendly. As said previously, they accommodated all of my wishes from start to finish of my stay, and the whole office from cleaner to manager also went out of their way to help me when I had been so stupid to leave something incredibly valuable behind in the flat.If I should put my finger on anything, it is probably that there are no elevators in the villas, so if you are staying at 3rd floor like me with a lot of luggage, that might take some time.But in my opinion, Hyde Park Suites is a really, really great place to stay for both families, couples and friends that want pleasant, central, trouble-free and affordable accommodation in London.	
